(SkillCatalog "General observation: observe target routes to the chosen sense/app, e.g. gameboy, glucose Patient, whatsapp, webcam, house, image IMAGE_ID, or audio AUDIO_ID")
(SkillHelp "observe" "observe target - route to the appropriate sense/app without acting")
(SkillHelp "observe" "Ambiguous targets return OBSERVE-UNKNOWN-TARGET instead of guessing.")
